CHECK:COMPARISON_TO_NULL: Comparison to NULL could be written "!str_area"
#48: FILE: fs/cifs/sess.c:375:
+	if (str_area == NULL) {

Comparisons to NULL in the form (foo == NULL) or (foo != NULL)
are better written as (!foo) and (foo).

